event ProposalCreated(uint256 id, address proposer, address[] targets, uint256[] values, string[] signatures, bytes[] calldatas, uint32 startBlock, uint32 endBlock, string description)
event VoteCast(address indexed voter, uint256 id, uint8 support, uint256 votes, string reason)
function actions() view returns (address[] targets, uint256[] values, string[] signatures, bytes[] calldatas)
function castVoteBySig(uint256 id, address voter, uint8 support, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s)
function castVoteWithReason(uint256 id, uint8 support, string reason)
function propose(address[] targets, uint256[] values, string[] signatures, bytes[] calldatas, string description) returns (uint256)
